item.title: CVE-2022-2535|2024-08-03T00:39:08.017Z -- unknown -- searchwp%20live%20ajax%20search
item.description: The SearchWP Live Ajax Search WordPress plugin before 1.6.2 does not ensure that users making a live search are limited to published posts only, allowing unauthenticated users to make a crafted query disclosing private/draft/pending post titles along with their permalink
